<plot>Ji-hae was abandoned by her parents as an infant and raised by and elderly man. Now an adult, she returns his kindness by taking care of him as his health fails. She meets Su-deol, a farmer in the village, and the two fall in love. However, because of her unwitting association with freedom fighters through Su-deol, Ji-hye finds herself hunted by the Japanese police</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?251124</url></doc>
